{"tid":1368672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一名台港人夢想係成為一個寵物小精靈訓練大師，我正式向你們挑戰。","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:22:08.000Z","uid":288337,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c06552fd7fc899f652ca3eb083eed38e2042b39a","tid":1368672,"uid":288337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"新來先報道<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oMdsxDS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoMdsxDS.png&h=f916760b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這麼多年我希望成為一個寵物小精靈大師的夢想從未熄滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近我從大木博士口中得知有一股惡勢力到處蔓延<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ECBNxHn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FECBNxHn.png&h=f0ad1543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加上聽說香港有比超夢夢更可怕的𨳒精靈，所以前來面聖。<br />\n明天我決定到香港著名的道館<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗警黑道館</span></span>捕捉當地稀有小精靈，以及讓你們瞧瞧我當年在台北市抓到的超高cp小精靈的厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0t0SGk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0t0SGk.png&h=ff2965fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港的訓練師們應該不會因為炎熱和害怕了我不敢出門吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ㄏㄏㄏㄏ"},{"pid":"ea158023fc8869b6f852b3ba58a28d3da015fcb4","tid":1368672,"uid":288337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"沒人敢回我俗辣"},{"pid":"3ee8d5f72c345827870adc06181968ea194b2c74","tid":1368672,"uid":261455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"係我眼中何妖只有鯉魚王級數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1be7878a8326d137ff98ed392aa6940c294c5df","tid":1368672,"uid":288337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"沒人敢回我俗辣"},{"pid":"685fdd0a56da7dd07